lockquote><blockquote><br />\n我都覺</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我行親去高層都有依種感覺<br />\n但又唔係想尋死</blockquote><br />\n畏高嘅人係會咁</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n應該係<br />\n但又有種衝動想一野跳出去<br />\n所以高層我係唔敢行得太出<br />\n更加唔好話企係玻璃望落去<br />\n但我估果期down 真係有機會就咁做傻事"},{"pid":"63ee63624a32138884dfd85ce7d74adc13452603","tid":34164,"uid":13421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T11:21:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>岩岩見到條屍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13525958d454e34e9306c24ea7ccad365c4dec1a","tid":34164,"uid":41524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T11:21:45.000Z","msg":"我都係,搭電梯反而驚跌落去<br />\n但去到六樓(好似,有漫畫果層)望落去會有衝動跳落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edf79cb7b91ec46da85654e843f7e5eec7e66eba","tid":34164,"uid":47463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T11:25:01.000Z","msg":"幢野咁樣衰 我見到都想死"},{"pid":"0c62f6e2ba0dc315c2672be5bda8257342c9ac02","tid":34164,"uid":26368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T11:28:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n我都覺</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我行親去高層都有依種感覺<br />\n但又唔係想尋死</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我記得APM又係有人咁講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我去親Apm 都有呢種感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n次次上去睇戲 係頂樓望翻落黎都會好想跳<br />\n係咪我壓力太大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/face